      "rationale": "Flow rates and rotational speeds in FDA GCBP experimental dataset matched CFD boundary conditions within 2.3% across all 5 adult operating points. Haematocrit held at 33% (bovine blood surrogate) consistent with original validation protocol. Expanded haematocrit range (36\u201342%) not covered by existing test conditions."
