      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model must be justified for the flow regime; Gradation 2 required.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark studies for centrifugal pump internal flows (Re ~ 1e5\u20135e5). Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model is the standard for regulatory CFD submissions. Model form justified at Gradation 2 for adult nominal flow regime. Applicability to low-Reynolds paediatric flows (Re ~ 4e4) not formally evaluated; flagged for re-validation scope."
